<title>dạyb qlby dạyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (dạyb qlby dạyb .. fy ạlʿsẖrẗ mʿạk
 jạy lk rby jạyb .. ṭyby wbạtrjạk)2
 1- (sẖạyfk yạ kẖlạṣy .. btmlạ bkẖmr kạsy
 fkry wạḥsạsy .. dạyb ạ̉nạ fyk
 sạmʿk btnạdyny .. frfʿt ʿyny
 ạ̉nẓrk tʿṭyny .. ạ̉srạr kẖạỷfyk)2
 2- (qlby byk mftwn .. byk rby mftwn
 wbḥbk mdywn .. nfsy ạ̉rd ạldyn
 ʿlmtny hwạk .. twʿd wạstnạk
 ạ̉nsy̱ ạlkl mʿạk .. bs ạ̹ḥnạ ạlạ̹tnyn)2
 3- (hạ ʿmry qạrwrẗ .. ṭyb byk mạ̉swrẗ
 qdmthạ mkswrẗ .. ʿnd qdmyk
 lytk trḍy byã .. bạlrwḥ tskn fyã
 wtmlk ʿlyã .. rạỷḥty tfwḥ byk)2</lyrics>
